import React from "react";

function VideoForm(props) {
	return (
		<form onSubmit={() => alert("load vid")}>
			<input
				name="videoUrl"
				type="text"
				onChange={props.handleFormChange}
				value={props.videoFormConfig.videoUrl}
			/>

			<input
				id="quality-1080"
				type="radio"
				value="1080p"
				name="quality"
				onChange={props.handleFormChange}
			/>
			<label htmlFor="quality-1080">1080p</label>

			<input
				id="quality-720"
				type="radio"
				value="720p"
				name="quality"
				onChange={props.handleFormChange}
			/>
			<label htmlFor="quality-720">720p</label>

			<input
				id="quality-360"
				type="radio"
				value="360p"
				name="quality"
				onChange={props.handleFormChange}
			/>
			<label htmlFor="quality-360">360p</label>

			<input
				id="quality-144"
				type="radio"
				value="144"
				name="quality"
				onChange={props.handleFormChange}
			/>
			<label htmlFor="quality-144">144p</label>

			<input disabled={props.isloadDisabled} type="submit" value="load" />
		</form>
	);
}

export default VideoForm;
